<article class="syl-article-base tt-article-content syl-page-article syl-device-pc">
<p data-track="1"><strong>导读：</strong>山竹是比较普遍的热带水果，它因为营养极高有着“水果皇后”的美称。可生食或者制做果脯，外果皮中的红色素可用来做染料。我们一起分享有关山竹的相关知识吧！</p>
<div class="pgc-img">
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-269" title="915406f3aa52416191e7a6d56d873ace" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/915406f3aa52416191e7a6d56d873ace.jpg" alt="915406f3aa52416191e7a6d56d873ace" width="400" height="225" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="2"><strong>01</strong></p>
<p data-track="3"><strong>山竹的基本知识</strong></p>
<p data-track="4">山竹原名莽吉柿，原产于东南亚，一般种植10年才开始结果，对环境要求非常严格，目前市面上的货一般是泰国山竹或马来西亚山竹。</p>
<p data-track="5">规格分为2A、3A、4A、5A、6A，数值越大，对应的果型就越大。</p>
<div class="pgc-img">
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-270" title="3239a46359dd41748620f3e70418fb7c" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/3239a46359dd41748620f3e70418fb7c.jpg" alt="3239a46359dd41748620f3e70418fb7c" width="929" height="603" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/3239a46359dd41748620f3e70418fb7c.jpg 929w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/3239a46359dd41748620f3e70418fb7c-300x195.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/3239a46359dd41748620f3e70418fb7c-768x498.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 929px) 100vw, 929px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<div class="pgc-img">
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-271" title="e92d85b09e854d8e94c98b0a2ca986b9" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/e92d85b09e854d8e94c98b0a2ca986b9.jpg" alt="e92d85b09e854d8e94c98b0a2ca986b9" width="1280" height="668" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/e92d85b09e854d8e94c98b0a2ca986b9.jpg 1280w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/e92d85b09e854d8e94c98b0a2ca986b9-300x157.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/e92d85b09e854d8e94c98b0a2ca986b9-1024x534.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/e92d85b09e854d8e94c98b0a2ca986b9-768x401.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="6">一般情况下，山竹可以分为三类。油竹、沙竹和花竹。</p>
<p data-track="7">油竹表面一般呈黑色，果皮光滑，卖相好。</p>
<div class="pgc-img">
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-272" title="02537b9e76274bf9bee180b05c764537" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/02537b9e76274bf9bee180b05c764537.jpg" alt="02537b9e76274bf9bee180b05c764537" width="978" height="928" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/02537b9e76274bf9bee180b05c764537.jpg 978w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/02537b9e76274bf9bee180b05c764537-300x285.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/02537b9e76274bf9bee180b05c764537-768x729.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 978px) 100vw, 978px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="8">沙竹，又叫麻竹。50年以上树龄才能产出的品种。和油竹相反，沙竹卖相很差，表皮不平，颜色类似于沙土，看着完全是另外的水果。但沙竹的口感却是所有山竹里最好的，产量也最少。</p>
<div class="pgc-img">
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-284" title="f0e69569bf3a4dd29bbe101f0f510d8e" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/f0e69569bf3a4dd29bbe101f0f510d8e.jpg" alt="f0e69569bf3a4dd29bbe101f0f510d8e" width="1264" height="678" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/f0e69569bf3a4dd29bbe101f0f510d8e.jpg 1264w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/f0e69569bf3a4dd29bbe101f0f510d8e-300x161.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/f0e69569bf3a4dd29bbe101f0f510d8e-1024x549.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/f0e69569bf3a4dd29bbe101f0f510d8e-768x412.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1264px) 100vw, 1264px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="9">花竹，又叫半油沙。介于油竹和沙竹之间，一般需15至50年树育出。</p>
<div class="pgc-img">
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-273" title="401801c0afe944f7b42fbbb044d154dd" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/401801c0afe944f7b42fbbb044d154dd.jpg" alt="401801c0afe944f7b42fbbb044d154dd" width="1264" height="870" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/401801c0afe944f7b42fbbb044d154dd.jpg 1264w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/401801c0afe944f7b42fbbb044d154dd-300x206.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/401801c0afe944f7b42fbbb044d154dd-1024x705.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/401801c0afe944f7b42fbbb044d154dd-768x529.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1264px) 100vw, 1264px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="10"><strong>关于萼片</strong></p>
<p data-track="11">山竹的底部有类似花瓣状的蒂瓣，通常是4-8片，蒂瓣的片数等于果肉的瓣数，不信你瞧瞧。</p>
<div class="pgc-img">
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-274" title="4f92e8f011b04c3faf352b4293959a34" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/4f92e8f011b04c3faf352b4293959a34.jpg" alt="4f92e8f011b04c3faf352b4293959a34" width="996" height="754" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/4f92e8f011b04c3faf352b4293959a34.jpg 996w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/4f92e8f011b04c3faf352b4293959a34-300x227.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/4f92e8f011b04c3faf352b4293959a34-768x581.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 996px) 100vw, 996px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="12">官方回答：果壳底部小瓣与果肉是由相同的体细胞发育而成，所以数目会一样。由于山竹是由营养细胞发育而成，底部的小瓣其实是花萼，一般植物的花萼在长出果实时，会脱落，而山竹的却完好保留下来。而花萼和果肉由相同的体细胞发育而成，所以我们只要看花萼的数量就可以知道果肉有几颗。</p>
<p data-track="13">不过，挑选山竹并非萼片越多越好。山竹好不好吃与底部萼片的数量无关。在挑选山竹时，关键要看它新鲜与否。</p>
<p data-track="14"><strong>02</strong></p>
<p data-track="15"><strong>山竹如何储存</strong></p>
<p data-track="16">山竹是呼吸跃变型果实，贮藏保鲜时间较短。</p>
<p data-track="17">采购回来的山竹，通常是用红框装的，山竹框的内层用油纸包裹，山竹在油纸内处于湿润密封状态，山竹上层用湿海绵覆盖。</p>
<div class="pgc-img">
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-275" title="54a3ab8ea74c45f7810bf39dce178b40" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/54a3ab8ea74c45f7810bf39dce178b40.jpg" alt="54a3ab8ea74c45f7810bf39dce178b40" width="1080" height="736" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/54a3ab8ea74c45f7810bf39dce178b40.jpg 1080w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/54a3ab8ea74c45f7810bf39dce178b40-300x204.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/54a3ab8ea74c45f7810bf39dce178b40-1024x698.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/54a3ab8ea74c45f7810bf39dce178b40-768x523.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="18">我们在进货回来后如果山竹库存多，需要将山竹整箱存储起来，放置在冷柜或者立风柜中，保证储存在相对低温的状态。</p>
<p data-track="19"><strong>03</strong></p>
<p data-track="20"><strong>山竹如何挑选</strong></p>
<p data-track="21">1、看果蒂。（就是山竹果实连接山竹枝的那里）。</p>
<p data-track="22">颜色越绿说明越新鲜。如果蒂叶颜色暗沉，表示此山竹已太老，不适宜吃了；如果果蒂颜色变褐色或者变黑，说明这个山竹放置时间太长了，有可能腐烂变质了。</p>
<div class="pgc-img">
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-277" title="5b76d78d92244c56ba9c809fe52da533" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/5b76d78d92244c56ba9c809fe52da533.jpg" alt="5b76d78d92244c56ba9c809fe52da533" width="1280" height="722" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/5b76d78d92244c56ba9c809fe52da533.jpg 1280w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/5b76d78d92244c56ba9c809fe52da533-300x169.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/5b76d78d92244c56ba9c809fe52da533-1024x578.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/5b76d78d92244c56ba9c809fe52da533-768x433.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="23">2、看颜色。山竹的外壳成熟的过程中，颜色依序为鲜红、深紫、深咖啡色，鲜红色的山竹还不够甜，深黑啡色的山竹则肉质太软，深紫色的山竹最好，甜度足够，肉质结实。</p>
<p data-track="24">3、捏果壳。用手轻轻捏一下山竹的果壳，可以捏的动、有弹性的则说明是新鲜的。如果太硬，捏不动，则是太老或风干了，这个山竹就不新鲜了。如果太软，则山竹可能被泡了或者腐烂了。</p>
<div class="pgc-img">
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-276" title="2b435acddaae49898a059178b4dcdfb9" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/2b435acddaae49898a059178b4dcdfb9.jpg" alt="2b435acddaae49898a059178b4dcdfb9" width="1280" height="718" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/2b435acddaae49898a059178b4dcdfb9.jpg 1280w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/2b435acddaae49898a059178b4dcdfb9-300x168.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/2b435acddaae49898a059178b4dcdfb9-1024x574.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/2b435acddaae49898a059178b4dcdfb9-768x431.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="25">4、掂分量看大小。大小合适均匀、分量比较重的山竹，一般水分比较多，够新鲜，也好吃。重量太轻的山竹，则可能是被风干了，已经不新鲜了。</p>
<div class="pgc-img">
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-278" title="6b12e55b3a3b422c90b18c3faecc28e8" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/6b12e55b3a3b422c90b18c3faecc28e8.jpg" alt="6b12e55b3a3b422c90b18c3faecc28e8" width="1280" height="720" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/6b12e55b3a3b422c90b18c3faecc28e8.jpg 1280w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/6b12e55b3a3b422c90b18c3faecc28e8-300x169.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/6b12e55b3a3b422c90b18c3faecc28e8-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/6b12e55b3a3b422c90b18c3faecc28e8-768x432.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="26"><strong>04</strong></p>
<p data-track="27"><strong>食用小tip</strong></p>
<p data-track="28">食用方法一般为压破掰开。</p>
<div class="pgc-img">
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-279" title="e3bc8a531c5a4f1ba94bac6b176db1a1" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/e3bc8a531c5a4f1ba94bac6b176db1a1.jpg" alt="e3bc8a531c5a4f1ba94bac6b176db1a1" width="640" height="796" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/e3bc8a531c5a4f1ba94bac6b176db1a1.jpg 640w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/e3bc8a531c5a4f1ba94bac6b176db1a1-241x300.jpg 241w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<div class="pgc-img">
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-280" title="d7daff855490492eb73331dca309ff9d" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/d7daff855490492eb73331dca309ff9d.jpg" alt="d7daff855490492eb73331dca309ff9d" width="640" height="804" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/d7daff855490492eb73331dca309ff9d.jpg 640w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/d7daff855490492eb73331dca309ff9d-239x300.jpg 239w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<div class="pgc-img">
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-281" title="9cb179ddbbb843c8af67fbad91bfdb75" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/9cb179ddbbb843c8af67fbad91bfdb75.jpg" alt="9cb179ddbbb843c8af67fbad91bfdb75" width="640" height="788" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/9cb179ddbbb843c8af67fbad91bfdb75.jpg 640w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/9cb179ddbbb843c8af67fbad91bfdb75-244x300.jpg 244w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="29">剥果壳时必须小心翼翼，格外留神，注意不要将紫色或红色的果壳汁液染在肉瓣上，因为它会影响口味，沾到衣服上也极难洗脱。</p>
<div class="pgc-img">
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-282" title="b05bc1dae12c43d09180a050ab92f826" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/b05bc1dae12c43d09180a050ab92f826.jpg" alt="b05bc1dae12c43d09180a050ab92f826" width="960" height="882" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/b05bc1dae12c43d09180a050ab92f826.jpg 960w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/b05bc1dae12c43d09180a050ab92f826-300x276.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/b05bc1dae12c43d09180a050ab92f826-768x706.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="30"><strong>1、山竹汁弄到衣服上怎么洗？</strong></p>
<p data-track="31">（1）用陈醋清洗被染到的地方</p>
<p data-track="32">（2）用水打湿染到的地方，用食盐涂抹，再用手反复轻搓，最后用清水清洗即可。</p>
<p data-track="33"><strong>2、适用人群</strong></p>
<p data-track="34">一般人都可食用。体弱、病后的人更适合，虽然一般人都可食用山竹，但每天吃3个足矣。因含糖分较高，肥胖者宜少吃，糖尿病者更应忌食。它亦含较高钾质，故肾病及心脏病人应少吃。</p>
<p data-track="35"><strong>3、孕妇吃山竹的注意事项</strong></p>
<p data-track="36">（1）山竹中糖分较高，因此妊娠高血压和妊娠糖尿病的孕妇不要吃。</p>
<p data-track="37">（2）山竹中含有较高钾质，患有肾病和心脏病的孕妇要少吃</p>
<p data-track="38">（3）山竹性寒凉，因此体质虚寒的孕妇要少吃</p>
<p data-track="39">（4）山竹富含纤维素，过多食用会引起便秘，便秘的孕妇要注意。</p>
<p data-track="40">（5）山竹不能喝和西瓜、豆浆、啤酒、白菜、芥菜、苦瓜、冬瓜荷叶汤等寒凉食物同吃，如果孕妇担心山竹的寒凉对身体有伤，可以煮着吃或是做菜，水果也可以入菜的。</p>
<p data-track="41">（6）孕妇能吃山竹，但是必定要注意数量和方法，每日食用山竹不超过3个为宜。</p>
